      <p>For sufficient ventilation make sure that the system placement
follows the minimum clearances. Make sure that the system environment
is within the specifications. For information about the environment
specifications, see the <i>Technical Data</i>.</p>
      <p>The necessary quantity of air cooling per hour from the cooling
system depends on:<ul>
            <li>
               <p>The size and number of systems</p>
            </li>
            <li>
               <p>The specified ambient temperature</p>
            </li>
            <li>
               <p>The temperature of the incoming cold air from the cooling system</p>
            </li>
         </ul>
      </p>
